          "uuid": "f3691b23-d7e7-4eaf-b9a5-03cc7c589110",
          "text": "During the year ended December 31, 2019, we recorded a total pre-tax charge of $5.0 million for severance and facility relocation associated with our manufacturing footprint consolidation and optimization, acquisition integration, and reorganization for business efficiency improvement. For the year ended December 31, 2018, we recorded total severance and related costs of $4.2 million. The cumulative costs recognized under this restructuring plan are $9.3 million.",
